{"tid":998610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唯美風呃Like？KOL野餐睇夜景　玩煙火險燒山】","createTime":"2019-01-28T05:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T05:58:33.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc384a6eb938c81044fcb4284dd00aefdca75ff","tid":998610,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>唯美風呃Like？KOL野餐睇夜景　玩煙火險燒山</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190128/bkn-20190128133523568-0128_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190128%2Fbkn-20190128133523568-0128_00822_001.html&d=%2B6PerixXDkZX5A3TLqthDhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1d6236b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190128/bkn-20190128133523568-0128_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190128/photo/bkn-20190128133523568-0128_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190128135550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190128133523568-0128_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190128135550&h=3e5422a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為咗呃Like可以去到幾盡？<br />\n<br />\n不少人為了影靚相呃Like，絞盡腦汁。最近有人上山看夜景時玩煙火，更將「美景」分享至社交平台，惹怒眾網民。<br />\n<br />\n有網民周日（27日）在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」發貼，指有年輕男子除夕夜在衞奕信徑第三段，拿着已點燃的「仙女棒」坐在野餐墊上興高采烈地拍照。相片其後上傳至其Instagram，以英文標註「繁星滿天的夜晚」，引來逾600人讚好。<br />\n<br />\n由於冬季風高物燥，燃點煙火隨時釀成山火。網民紛紛怒斥︰「最憎呢類為呃like而影相嘅KOL」、「燒死佢自己冇問題，唔該唔好累山頭上住嘅其他動物」。現時該男子已刪除有關相片。<br />\n<br />\n根據《危險品條例》，非法藏有煙花爆竹的最高刑罰為罰款25000港元及監禁6個月。另在郊野地區，郊遊人士應在指定地點生火，隨意生火，可被檢控，罰款可高達25000元及監禁1年。"},{"pid":"482400b46d4e53bbef7bb0c00d9e78d3db526ec1","tid":998610,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"好似係某cctbb奀星嘅細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}